---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Configuration - LrGeniusAI">
  <section class="configuration-section">
    <h1>Configuration</h1>
    <p>This page describes the configuration settings for the LrGeniusAI plugin.</p>

    <h2>API Keys / Provider Configuration</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Gemini API key:</strong> Required for using Google Gemini cloud models. <a href="https://aistudio.google.com/app/api-keys">Obtain from Google AI Studio</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>ChatGPT API key:</strong> Required for using OpenAI ChatGPT models. <a href="https://platform.openai.com/api-keys">Obtain from OpenAI</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Prompts</h2>
    <p>Edit prompts sent to the AI, if needed. This is an advanced topic. In most cases you can stick to the standard prompt.</p>

    <h2>Export Settings</h2>
    <p>Export settings:</strong> Modifies settings for the reduced-size export used by the plugin to the AI.</p>

  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .configuration-section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
